  Short description: PTZ dome integrations are preloaded with admin/12345, giving attackers control of downstream devices and pivot paths.
  Vulnerable code snippet (≤40 lines):

  21702		<UserName>admin</UserName>
  21703		<Passwd>12345</Passwd>
  21704		<HttpPort>80</HttpPort>

  Repro steps:
