  PoC?: Yes – four dome slots expose the same credential tuple.
  Remediation: Require operators to enroll PTZ endpoints with per-device strong credentials and reject default values at runtime.
  Severity (CVSS 3.1 AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:U/C:H/I:H/A:N): 8.2 High
  Tools & versions used: sed (BSD)

